                   <div class=\"card-title\">\n                                    <img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"72\" height=\"72\" src=\"https:\/\/Tech Chicago.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/target-04.png\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"\" \/>                                    <h3>Project Scope <\/h3>\n                                <\/div>\n                                <p class=\"desc\">\n                                    A payments provider wanted to better showcase their offers for public transportation companies and improve CX.                                <\/p>\n                            <\/div>\n                                                    <div class=\"card\">\n                                <div class=\"card-title\">\n                                    <img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"72\" height=\"72\" src=\"https:\/\/Tech Chicago.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/puzzle-piece-02.png\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"\" \/>                                    <h3>Services Provided <\/h3>\n                                <\/div>\n                                <p class=\"desc\">\n                                    UX audit, technical audit, platform redesign, integrations                                <\/p>\n                            <\/div>\n                                                    <div class=\"card\">\n                                <div class=\"card-title\">\n                                    <img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"72\" height=\"72\" src=\"https:\/\/Tech Chicago.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/data.png\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"\" \/>                                    <h3>Technologies used <\/h3>\n                                <\/div>\n                                <p class=\"desc\">\n                                    Node, Yarn, Typescript\u000bNextJs, ReactJs, AWS                                <\/p>\n                            <\/div>\n                                            <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/section>\n    \n\n            <section class='section business-challenge'>\n            <div class=\"wrap\">\n                <div class=\"section-header centered\">\n                                            <h2 >The Business Challenge<\/h2>\n                                                                <p>LittlePay wanted to better showcase their offers for public transportation companies, improve the visibility of certain features and all-in-all create a swifter customer experience.<\/p>\n                                    <\/div>\n                <div class=\"arrow\">\n                    <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/Tech Chicago.io\/wp-content\/themes\/esc-info\/img\/svg-icons\/arrow-narrow-down-grey.svg\" alt=\"arrow grey\">\n                <\/div>\n                <div class=\"our-solution\">\n                    <div class=\"top-box\">\n                                                    <h2 >The Solution<\/h2>\n                                                                            <p>We performed a UX and technical audit of the existing platform, identified potential improvements beyond the way it looks. Then, together with the client decided on the action plan: redesigning all the existing flows of the platform with new goals in mind, refactored existing features with the goal of enhancing the user experience. We built several features in both the Merchant&#8217;s and Traveler&#8217;s portal.<\/p>\n                                            <\/div>\n                                    <\/div>\n                            <\/div>\n        <\/section>\n    \n\n            <section class='section business-impact'>\n            <div class=\"wrap\">\n                                    <h2 class='title-bg'>Business Impact<\/h2>\n                                                    <div class=\"desc\"><p>The face-lift of the platform&#8217;s UI resulted in higher user engagement rates for all systems: merchant, riders and devices and improved the platforms security. The company plans to extend their service offers to new geographies having gained the confidence that their platform can easily adapt to new business context.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n                                <div class=\"contact-box\">\n                                                        <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/section>\n    \n\n            <section class='section tech-stack'>\n            <div class=\"wrap\">\n                <div class=\"section-header centered full\">\n                                            <h2>Tech Stack<\/h2>\n                                                        <\/div>\n\n                <div class=\"table \">\n                                            <div class=\"row\">\n                                                            <div class=\"title\">\n                                    Front End                                <\/div>\n                                                                                    <div class=\"list\">\n                                                                <div class=\"item\">\n                                                                            <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/Tech Chicago.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/Frame-14.svg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"\" \/>                                                                                                                <span>React<\/span>\n                                                                    <\/div>\n                                                                <div class=\"item\">\n                                                                            <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/Tech Chicago.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/Typescrip.svg\" class=\"attachment-full size